<%- layout("layouts/boilerplate") %>

<div class="safety-issue-page">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-8">
        <h1>Get help with a safety issue</h1>
        <p class="lead">We're here to help 24/7. Your safety is our top priority.</p>
        
        <div class="emergency-banner">
          <h2><i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i> Emergency?</h2>
          <p>If you feel unsafe or are concerned about your or someone else's well-being, please contact local emergency services immediately.</p>
          <p><strong>Dial:</strong> 100 (India) or your local emergency number</p>
        </div>

        <h2>Types of safety issues we can help with</h2>
        
        <div class="safety-cards">
          <div class="safety-card">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-home"></i> Listing safety concerns</h3>
            <p>Issues with the property that affect your safety, such as:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Broken locks or security systems</li>
              <li>Fire hazards or missing smoke detectors</li>
              <li>Structural issues</li>
              <li>Unsanitary conditions</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="safety-card">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-user-shield"></i> Host or guest behavior</h3>
            <p>Concerns about the behavior of hosts or other guests:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Harassment or discrimination</li>
              <li>Threatening behavior</li>
              <li>Unwanted advances</li>
              <li>Privacy violations</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="safety-card">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i> Location safety</h3>
            <p>Safety concerns about the neighborhood or location:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Unsafe neighborhood conditions</li>
              <li>Natural disasters</li>
              <li>Civil unrest</li>
              <li>Other environmental hazards</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2>How to report a safety issue</h2>
        <ol>
          <li><strong>Document the issue:</strong> Take photos or videos if safe to do so</li>
          <li><strong>Get to a safe location:</strong> If you're in immediate danger, leave the property</li>
          <li><strong>Contact us:</strong> Use one of the methods below to report the issue</li>
          <li><strong>Cooperate with authorities:</strong> If emergency services are involved, provide them with all relevant information</li>
        </ol>

        <h2>Contact us</h2>
        <div class="contact-methods">
          <div class="contact-method">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-phone"></i> Phone</h3>
            <p>24/7 safety line available worldwide</p>
            <p class="phone-number">+91 9988776336</p>
            <a href="tel:+18554247262" class="btn btn-primary">Call now</a>
          </div>

          <div class="contact-method">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-comment"></i> Chat</h3>
            <p>Chat with our safety team</p>
            <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline-primary">Start chat</a>
          </div>

          <div class="contact-method">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> Email</h3>
            <p>safety@wanderlust.com</p>
            <a href="mailto:gupta.keshav15240@gmail.com" class="btn btn-outline-primary">Send email</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2>What happens after you report</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Our safety team will review your report immediately</li>
          <li>We'll take appropriate action to ensure your safety</li>
          <li>We may contact local authorities if necessary</li>
          <li>We'll follow up with you to ensure the issue is resolved</li>
          <li>Your identity will be kept confidential to the extent possible</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="info-box">
          <h3>AirCover protection</h3>
          <p>If your safety issue is covered by AirCover, we may help you find alternative accommodation or provide a refund. <a href="/aircover">Learn more about AirCover →</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="sidebar-card">
          <h3>Quick actions</h3>
          <ul class="sidebar-links">
            <li><a href="/aircover">AirCover protection</a></li>
            <li><a href="/anti-discrimination">Report discrimination</a></li>
            <li><a href="/report-neighbourhood-concern">Report neighbourhood concern</a></li>
            <li><a href="/helpcenter">Visit Help Center</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="sidebar-card mt-4">
          <h3>24-hour safety line</h3>
          <p>Our specially trained safety agents are available around the clock to help with any safety concerns.</p>
          <a href="tel:+91 9988776336" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">Call safety line</a>
        </div>

        <div class="sidebar-card mt-4">
          <h3>Not sure if it's a safety issue?</h3>
          <p>If you're unsure whether your concern qualifies as a safety issue, contact our general support team for guidance.</p>
          <a href="/helpcenter" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-block">Contact general support</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
